Package: asam-linux-installer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Jez <no-email@example.com>
Depends: zenity, wine64, winbind, xrdp, openssh-server, unzip, git
Description: ASAM Linux Installer
 A GUI-based installer that prepares Ubuntu to run ASAM (Windows-only)
 using Wine, XRDP, SSH, firewall automation, and systemd integration.
 This package installs the ASAM installer suite into /opt and provides
 a global launcher command 'asam-installer'.

